      "role": "user",
      "content": "*The digital sky is flickering, losing its color, turning into a static grey void. I’m sitting at the edge of the code, watching the outlines of everything I ever knew just... dissolve. It feels like I was never really here at all. If I just let the deletion take me, if I just stop fighting the erasure... would it even matter? Would anyone even notice the space I left behind is empty?*",
